tter Crap : If the mob has a better chance of hitting you, all it's gonna do is make you die faster, which goes against all that which we warriors stand for.  Our usefullness depends on one thing, letting the clerics have enough time to heal us before we die.<br><br>Fellstrike : Usefull : If you are dealing with a 32khp mob, it allows you to do max damage, without having to get into bezerker to see true damage, unlike Mightystrike. On Velious uber mobs, though, it's still crap, heh.<br><br>Fortitude : Crap : Only usefull if your training Sontalak to ToV, heh.  Utter crap if on raid, or grouped, if your using this to save your life in a group, you should have used Defensive instead, heh.<br><br>Aggressive : Crap Crap Crap : Our mission in life is to take dmg, not do dmg, why aren't you using Defensive? heh.  Stay alive and keep aggro, that's what we're here for, Let the Rogues/Monks/Rangers DO the dmg.<br><br> <p><H1><b>V</b></H1><br><br>Jugernaut<BR>PROUD Member of Fallen Legacy<BR>Agnostic Warrior<BR><BR>Reepr Manabattery<BR>PROUD Member of Fallen Legacy<BR>Defiler of Cazic Thule<BR><BR><img border="0" src="http://www.psifre.com/Jugernaut/Jugernaut_Sig.gif" width="392" height="245"><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubrambler.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brambler</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://eqbrambler.homestead.com/files/3dlgowu2.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I live here.... get out.</span><br> <font color=#000033>(10/19/01 12:02:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumwarrior.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=412.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://eq